            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/3-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Remove</strong> the pan from the heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Serve</strong> the risotto topped with roasted vegetables and a drizzle of olive oil</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
